³   - Must   be  taken  from  the  episode, i.e.-   not   encoded  separately ³
³   - Stream  samples  are  recommended  for  any questionable issue with the ³
³     source, e.g. no IVTC possible, IVTC to 24.975fps, etc.                  ³
